captions.text: What do you expect to get from life?
What do you expect get from your businesses?
What do you expect to get from your relationships?
What is it that you expect from...
That have a strong sense of self approval
Alot of people don't expect much from life
So they don't shoot for much
They are not preparing for much
Alot people just showing up in life
Alot of people just get up in the morning
Just to pull a checkdown watching
So you wanna be a different kind of person
You want to get something out of this
If you are going to do it
You got some expectations from this
But don't be afraid of making decisions
You can't be paralysed by fear
Of failure or you will never push yourself
You keep pushing because you believe in yourself
And you know that it is the right thing to do
So don’t be afraid to fail!

comments.text:
I finally found the guts today to close my past and to start a new age.
There is so much pain, fear and frustration.
Yet I still am Brave enough to do something about and to move forward.
From this point in life, (again) I refuse to go back. 
From this point I will only move forward. 
I will learn how to be strong again on my own.
On my own I will teach myself again how to control my powers within.
Because I simply still do believe in my happy ending.

This video, gave me the inspiration to write a little speech about it.
I said it to FB and all the other social media. Goodbye.
I'll be back one day. Soon I'll rejoin my Brothers and Sisters in our quest 
to freedom.
Here it goes: 

Close the past
Be one with the moon and the sun.
Create your own light in the darkness.
Learn how to survive.

Run, fight, live with the Wolves.

A new Age will Rise.
Rise out of the Ashes.

Stronger, faster, better
Rise with Dawn

Enter the void.
Be one with the Darkness.
Be Light﻿
